{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","role":"symbol","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false,"name":"iOS","deprecated":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false}],"title":"OUDSRadioItem"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:additionalLabel:helper:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations"}],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"text":": like the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The radio indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isError: true,","                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","level":2},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange"}]},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"text":"Sosh","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.3.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","style":"note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"component_radioItem_Wireframe":{"alt":"A radio item component in light and dark mode with Wireframe theme","type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_radioItem_Wireframe.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools","alt":"A radio item component in light and dark mode with Orange Business Tools theme"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadio":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActi